    "description": "Easy to play, easy to retry.<br />\r\nFastRogue is a traditional rogue-&quot;like&quot; (including many items and monsters) but customized to be able to play for a short time (about 30-40min to clear).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nComplete the dungeon to pump up, and attack the Demon Castle.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game includes several rule valuations.<br />\r\n30+ items and 40+ monsters contains.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChallenge failure? No problem, you gain a power-up item according to the score.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat is rogue-like?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnter the dungeon and complete the deepest floor.<br />\r\nThe dungeon changes every time, for example, items, monster placement, traps, and shops.<br />\r\nRequires flexible response. Think and choose the most valuable action.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStory<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the otherworld, sword and magic otherworld.<br />\r\nThe evil demon dominates this world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOne time, a young woman, who trains to defeat evil, meets a suspicious man.<br />\r\nThe man says,<br />\r\n&quot;Please enter this dungeon. You will power up very much.<br />\r\nYou have the talent to gain power from the dungeon.&quot;<br />\r\nShe doubts the man, but she has no guess to power up.<br />\r\nShe decides to enter the dungeon.",
